Note: Named arguments must reorder based on parameter declaration.
Note: subtract(a=10, b=3) = 7. Caller writes args in REVERSE order using names.
Note: Expected exit code: 7

Process called "subtract" takes a as Integer, b as Integer returns Integer:
    Return a minus b
End Process

Process called "main" returns Integer:
    Let result be subtract with b as 3, a as 10
    Return result
End Process
